AIM_KINGDOM BY UNREAL This map was made for ONLAN KINGDOM SERIES, its basicly a remake of the normal aim_map with improved looks. (www.online-kingdom.org) New features:
  • light_environment;
  • env_sun;
  • de_train theme;
  • better ambience;
  • background sounds;
  • many more...
I hope you enjoy playing it, have fun!
